---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="How it works" description="How ServicesInMyCity and Rocco help homeowners find trusted pros and get the job done right.">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>How it works</h1>
      <p class="lede">No accounts. No runaround. Just ask Rocco.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="container" style="padding:40px 20px 64px">
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card"><h3>1. Tell Rocco what's going on</h3><p>Start with your city and the problem. No sign-up, no password &mdash; just type.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>2. Rocco helps you understand it</h3><p>He asks the right questions and explains things plainly. He equips you; he never diagnoses.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>3. Find nearby pros</h3><p>Rocco can surface nearby businesses from Google for your area &mdash; shown honestly, never as paid rankings.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>4. Decide with confidence</h3><p>Walk into the conversation informed so you don't overpay for work you don't need.</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="disclaimer" style="margin-top:24px">
      Recommendations are earned, never purchased. We never fabricate reviews, ratings, or contractor counts.
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
